 {r}←CreateTrigger dummy;body;name
⍝ Create a trigger that sends an event 9999 to AcreLog's main Form whenever acre's log variable changes.
 r←⍬
 body←'WatchAcreLog arg;html;⎕IO;⎕ML' ':Implements Trigger log' '⎕IO←1 ⋄ ⎕ML←1' ':Trap 6'
 name←({⍵↓⍨-≢##.APLTreeUtils.Last ⍵}1⊃⎕XSI),'n.TheForm'   ⍝ Has to work frorm both # (project is opened!) and ⎕SE (runtime)!
 body,←⊂'⎕NQ ',name,' 9999 arg.NewValue'
 body,←⊂':EndTrap'
 ⎕SE.acre._code.MP.⎕FX body
⍝Done
